      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Over lunch, Daniel and I planned out what we would do during our remaining few hours in Oxford. We decided to go tour two of the colleges next: "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "strong"
              }
            ],
            "text": "Christ Church"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " and "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "strong"
              }
            ],
            "text": "Magdalen"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ". Both of these colleges charge an admission fee ranging from $7 to $10 depending on the season."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "I didn't get very many pictures at Magdalen College because it was pouring rain at the time, but I got several at Christ Church. We toured the Great Hall, the cathedral, and other common areas. It would be very cool to be a student there!"
          }
        ]
