                  "title": null
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " Blackwell's Norrington Room in Oxford[/caption]"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Before heading back to the train station, we decided to grab dinner at the pub that our friend recommended, "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "strong"
              }
            ],
            "text": "Turf Tavern"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ". It had a fun, cozy atmosphere. Our favorite dish of the evening was the Scotch eggs (see below). Yum!"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
