        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "And that was our day in Oxford! My only regrets are not attending Evensong at one of the college's chapels and and not visiting The Kilns, the home of C.S. Lewis and the location where he wrote the Narnia books. We just didn't have enough time that day to do everything. However, I've heard that both are excellent experiences."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "That was our last day trip from Bristol. Our next stop was Watford to do the Warner Brothers Studio Tour of the Harry Potter film sets! Stay tuned!"
          }
        ]
